*** Ask us about the renovation credit ***

Step into your cozy haven! This charming 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence spans 1,888 square feet and rests on a generous 1-acre lot, providing ample space for outdoor enjoyment. With a new roof and HVAC system, this home offers worry-free living, allowing you to focus on the things that matter most. Don't miss the chance to make this your forever home - come experience the warmth and comfort it offers!
